Description: MultiFlexi RaiffeisenBank credential prototype
 RaiffeisenBank Premium API credential prototype for MultiFlexi core.
 Provides the CredentialProtoType class that defines account number,
 certificate and API client configuration fields.

Package: multiflexi-raiffeisenbank-ui
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, multiflexi-raiffeisenbank (= ${binary:Version}), multiflexi-web
Description: MultiFlexi RaiffeisenBank UI components
 RaiffeisenBank connection dialog for MultiFlexi web interface.
 Displays certificate validity, issuer information, rate limits
 and other technical details in the credential configuration form.
